# Psychological Engagement Features — Build Plan

## Context

10 active mutual friends, word-of-mouth growth. Four features chosen to create daily pull, social comparison, and emotional investment. Each feature is independent and can be built one at a time.

**Build order:** Streaks → Daily Prompts → Emoji Reactions → Weekly Recap

Streaks and Prompts are additive (no existing code migration). Reactions replaces the like system (bigger migration). Recap is built last so it queries whatever the final engagement table is (likes or reactions).

