### Edge cases
- Multiple publishes/day: only first counts (checks `last_publish_date === today`)
- Reposts: do NOT count (only `uploadJournalContentService` path)
- Editing existing journal: does NOT count (only new journal insert path)
- Draft chapters: only count on first `status → published` transition

