## Feature 2: Daily Writing Prompts

**Psychology:** Shared ritual — gives everyone a reason to open the app and a common topic to riff on.

### Database

```sql
CREATE TABLE writing_prompts (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    prompt_text TEXT NOT NULL,
    category TEXT DEFAULT 'general',
    created_at TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now()
);

ALTER TABLE journals ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS prompt_id INTEGER
    REFERENCES writing_prompts(id) ON DELETE SET NULL;

CREATE INDEX idx_journals_prompt_id ON journals(prompt_id) WHERE prompt_id IS NOT NULL;
```

Seed with ~150 prompts. Rotation: `dayOfYear % promptCount`, ordered by `id ASC` — deterministic, no cron needed, all users see the same prompt each day.

