## Verification (per feature)

**Streaks:** Publish a post → check sidebar/profile shows flame + count. Publish next day → streak increments. Skip a day → streak resets (or freeze used). Hit day 7 → milestone toast with confetti.

**Prompts:** Load home feed → prompt card appears at top. Click "Write your take" → editor opens with prompt context. Save → post shows prompt badge. Prompt card shows response count.

**Reactions:** Hover like button → picker appears with 6 emojis. Select fire → button shows 🔥 + count updates. Open ContentView → see per-type breakdown. Check notification shows "reacted 🔥 to your post". Quick tap toggles heart.

**Recap:** Load home feed on any day → recap card appears at top. Shows personal stats + group highlights. Click dismiss → card hidden. Refresh → stays hidden (localStorage). New week → reappears.
